{"title":"怀念一个人","authors":["涂强"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":1,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀念一个人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂强"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要说起大庆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就会想起一个人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个人离开我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经很远了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的孩子的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能从厚厚的教科书中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读到他的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月的烟云和尘土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湮没不了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代人如火的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少年过去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要说起大庆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就会自豪地想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个并非铁打的铁人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和一面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永不褪色的旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年很多挎着相机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔洋远眺的蓝眼睛们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是通过小小的一块古陶片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了解旭日初升的中国的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到钢铁井架"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在积雪的荒野刺破青天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色原油水一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自冻土深处喷吐而出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们才惊讶地发现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚细亚中国　不仅仅盛产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们喜欢的脆薄透明的瓷器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且还盛产一种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韧性的极富铁质的东西"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄肤色的中国人管这叫骨气＊"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}